<div class="container">
    <h1 class="mainText">About Us</h1>
    <hr class="themeHorizontal" />
    <div class="frontRow">
        <p>
            Here at Dough Boys we strive to bring you high quality artisan doughnuts. We are very proud of what
            we produce here.  Our doughnuts come from quality ingredients sourced from our local community.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="frontRow">
        <div class="frontCol">
            <div class="imgContainer"><img id="mapImg" src="~/images/map_location.png" /></div>
        </div>

        <div class="frontCol">
            We are conveniently located at 1 UNF Dr, Jacksonville, FL 32224, this is our first
            location and we hope to expand within the community.  We chose this location because
            it is near the beach and commercial areas. Come and stop by to grab some of our specialty doughnuts.
        </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="mainText">Mission Statement</h2>
    <div class="frontRow">
        <p>
            All of our products shall be of the highest quality and value provided with outstanding personal services at the lowest possible prices. All of our products and services shall be delivered consistently
            and measured one satisfied customer at a time, in superior, clean, convenient, fun and friendly neighborhood environments.
            We pledge to make Dough Boys the best place to eat and the best place to work.
        </p>
    </div>
</div>